text: Cycloponympha hermione is a moth in the Lyonetiidae family. It is known from Xinavane, Mozambique. This species has a wingspan of 9 mm. Head and antennae are white, the forewings are white with the costal edge dark fuscous towards base and some pale ochreous suffusions and grey marks. ==Related pages== *List of moths of Mozambique ==References== Category:Lyonetiidae
title: Cycloponympha hermione
